rc=\"https://na.cx/i/Hh6wcP2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHh6wcP2.jpg&h=d0c92abd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"242e3617c60ed347c0b06097ad8dad5f0229d931","tid":1553861,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gA6VhKYNvcY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgA6VhKYNvcY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=e4e08704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gA6VhKYNvcY&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"d6f4328711c573e9a031fe6e491f88038f7a342c","tid":1553861,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a05d2363c75d21655c5679fa45a2c218315ba5c5","tid":1553861,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T20:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d44f878362f4e514b0ce07f7bdabd34c73bd095e","tid":1553861,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T21:25:03.000Z","msg":"[警察文宣海報製作idea]<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n共產黨操控香港後，清算警隊便近了。你能逃過清算嗎？<br />\n養你的成本，比大陸武警高七倍，你又已經失去利用價值，為甚麼要留低你浪費米飯？<br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n共產黨操控香港後，清算警隊便近了。你能逃過清算嗎？<br />\n清算，輕則抄魷，重則送中死刑。<br />\n<br />\n3. <br />\n共產黨操控香港後，清算警隊便近了。你能逃過清算嗎？<br />\n清算了你，共產黨將會獲得香港人的掌聲，你覺得它會不會顧念你呢？<br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n共產黨操控香港後，清算警隊便近了。你能逃過清算嗎？<br />\n不要忘了你旁邊的好兄弟，今日你做的一舉一動他都看在眼裏，清算來臨時，最博命揭你陰私既，你覺得會是誰呢？"},{"pid":"c22a38b8d2d528a1e188217a090c97c660dd0a38","tid":1553861,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7533f6ff1667ab40068ffe2e037a1314f44f7f31","tid":1553861,"uid":285915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"最近好似好多人話英文嘅文宣唔夠，又話鬼佬想睇到啲翻譯左嘅新聞。其實又班香港人已經做緊架啦。<br />\n（跪求幫推） 其實香港有班人好努力做翻譯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545086</a><br />\n我哋網站叫<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=a31f8b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com</a>，我哋每日都會將香港嘅新聞翻譯再放上fb，tg，同埋twitter。小弟p牌冇得推po，唯有靠大家幫手推到外國人都知香港發生咩事。<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fcategory%2FCommunity-Organization%2FBeWater-HK-2406628919558580&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=e9ca9dae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhkg%2F%3Figshid%3Dwe1lffxlqh9f&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=377a257d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/bewaterhkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fbewaterhkg&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=ae3160b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/bewaterhkg</a>"},{"pid":"42f7d398e3e9746367bca4ef0b687b3ec00c4e1a","tid":1553861,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:52:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"527862f3b5e3729fa3a6bd39c144eed0588f4044","tid":1553861,"uid":227405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:33:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6b2c682250529709201366e50961c9aceb8300b8","tid":1553861,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":